We implemented middleware-based rate limiting to protect the system from excessive traffic. It restricts the number of requests per IP within a fixed time window and returns a 429 response if exceeded. Since it operates at the Rack layer, it blocks requests before they reach controllers or the database, improving performance and protecting application resources.

